{"tid":648052,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線架!!成堆大快活打手日日開post吹奏","createTime":"2018-04-30T10:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T12:51:40.000Z","uid":105746,"like":37,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7c7100a08071233862de97175b4c4b50a58ba6","tid":648052,"uid":105746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:53:11.000Z","msg":"我只可以講句 一定要試 係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要試!!</span></strong><br />\n佢已經打破左一般快餐嘅框架<br />\n一塊厚過你胸肌嘅雞胸竟然可以切得輕輕鬆鬆<br />\n咬落去仲鬆軟過女朋友對波<br />\n而從未食過伴碟蔬菜嘅我行出左第一步<br />\n小小鹽小小蒜令到蔬菜嘅鮮甜增加<br />\n係你食完菜之後你會發現<br />\n原來蔬菜嘅蒜汁同南瓜汁mix埋一齊<br />\n整個飯嘅層次又再提升<br />\n健康嘅美食真係要推上米芝蓮先得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/185245_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F185245_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=02ef2fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/185254_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F185254_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4bc13be2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"860a326a4f9a38d962e9f2446f42d06bdea97728","tid":648052,"uid":105746,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"希望嚟緊會試嘅一眾巴絲打<br />\n都可以開個post<br />\n推到上新假期推出國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db72b5e374933b8a26c0690a96a51fd3102b9be0","tid":648052,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:04:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a15c51595833b95f481113f801c452dd66a0bcd7","tid":648052,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a628fda5b68a16d7b9bf5bf9f7abd65645e60c4d","tid":648052,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":